19 SUMMARY
2200 This amendment adds a definition of "mobile dental services." It also requires the
2211 Department of Health and Human Services to ensure that the training and education to
2222 primary care providers on minimally invasive dental disease treatment for infants and small
2233 children is provided by licensed dental health professionals. The amendment also adds an
2244 appropriations and allocations section.
